item.description: Introduction: Welcome Back to Summoner’s Rift! For review, League of Legends(LoL) is a team based multiplayer online battle arena game where two teams of 5 battle to see who destroys the base first. There are 5 positions corresponding to the 3 map lanes: Top, Mid, Bot(Support and Attack Damage Carry or ADC), and Jungle(they roam). Often the characters(Champions) have specific classes that are associated with the position they are suited for.
